    texts, play this card with the play cost reduced by 11.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    [When Attacking] [Once Per Turn] Delete 2 other unsuspended Digimon.\n[All Turns]
    [Once Per Turn] When any of your other Digimon or Tamers are deleted, trash your
    opponent's top security card and return 1 of their Digimon with the lowest DP
    to the bottom of the deck."
